Class City

  • java.lang.Object
    • yt30_lp28.sengokugame.serverSide.City

  • public class City
extends java.lang.Object
    The java class for city entity; Note that City Entity is only used on serverSide. City can generate lighter, serializable CityIcon, which is transmitted to clientSide.

    lp28, yt30
